{"tid":1509990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"膠官：玻璃燈柱重要過大眾市民","createTime":"2019-08-27T04:25:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T05:55:32.000Z","uid":23302,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef25473a3e901d0de0112f35b56923f89fe7c2fc","tid":1509990,"uid":23302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:25:24.000Z","msg":"有示威者在觀塘遊行中，於九龍灣拆毁及破壞智慧燈柱，創科局長楊偉雄在政府跨部門記者會上形容，本月24日是「香港創科的黑暗一日」。民政事務局長劉江華表示，有市民問他示威者破壞燈柱與反修例的關係為何。<br />\n<br />\n楊偉雄稱，有示威者罔顧事實，強行說智慧燈柱侵犯個人私隱，公然破壞燈柱，令人痛心。他表示，局方已成立專責委員會，透過第三方獨立檢視，強調智慧燈柱工程在陽光下進行，絕不會侵犯個人私隱，承諾智慧燈柱不會流傳任何原始數據，希望市民能客觀對待。<br />\n<br />\n劉江華表示，有市民看到示威者在九龍灣拆毁燈柱的情況，問「燈柱和修例有什麼關係」，公眾非常憂慮和希望盡快停止暴力行為。<br />\n<br />\nSource:明報<br />\n林奠就對智能燈柱表示痛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但對受傷嘅義士就係叫佢同狗方聯絡自我送頭<br />\n一個政府並非為大眾去做實事<br />\n想建立管治信心都難啦 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efa245ff4d8756f91dacb74bfe23b7a4bbb6576","tid":1509990,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:25:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">831 雙真普選大遊行</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwUTenp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwUTenp.jpg&h=516e7a70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nCFSuVL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnCFSuVL.png&h=3e3a93bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfmm7Hr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxfmm7Hr.jpg&h=0e330442&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3db19ddb6d69e2564dddcef83791991174a34ca0","tid":1509990,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T04:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br /